articles.title: Newly discovered asteroid will bypass Earth - Voice of America
articles.description: Small chance asteroid could be on a course to strike the moon
articles.content:
Earth is not in danger of being hit by an asteroid in the near future, NASA and the European Space Agency said Tuesday.
